(NULL, 'Raja Parba is a unique festival of Odisha that celebrates what?', 'Harvest season', 'Menstruation and fertility of Earth', 'Monsoon arrival', 'New Year', 'B', 1, 'Festivals', 'medium', '["Raja Parba", "Fertility Festival", "Women Festival"]'::jsonb, 'Raja Parba is a three-day festival celebrating menstruation and fertility of Mother Earth. During this time, the earth is believed to be menstruating and is given rest.'),
