(NULL, 'Odissi is a classical dance form that originated from which temple?', 'Konark Sun Temple', 'Jagannath Temple, Puri', 'Lingaraj Temple', 'Mukteswar Temple', 'B', 1, 'Traditional Arts', 'medium', '["Odissi Dance", "Classical Dance", "Puri"]'::jsonb, 'Odissi dance originated from the Jagannath Temple in Puri, where temple dancers called Maharis performed devotional dances.'),
